  service-role values (Foundations / founder territory), so I cannot
  actually sign up, log in, fetch `/api/profiles/me`, or save a
  profile against a real backend. Verification is currently
  type-check + lint + unit tests + audit against the published
  contract. Same blocker the Auth, Database, and Core API agents
  recorded for this phase.

- **Stand up the Maps / Places integration for service-area picking.**
  Phase-1 task list scopes the Frontend to sign-up / mode-select +
  companion profile setup; map-based location selection on
  discovery / restaurant search arrives in Phase 2 once the
  Integrations agent publishes `/lib/maps`. The current service-area
  picker is a numeric lat/lng pair plus a "Use my current location"
